// COMPOSITE-DISABLING-CERT-VALIDATION — CWE-295 (Tier 16).
//
// Pourquoi : `rejectUnauthorized: false` (https/tls/axios) ou
// `strictSSL: false` (request) desactive la validation du certificat
// serveur — MITM trivial, le client accepte n'importe quel cert.
//
// Source : extractors/security-patterns.ts (Tier 16).
// Fact : TlsConfigUnsafe(file, line, key, containingSymbol)
//
// References :
//   - https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/295.html
//   - CodeQL js/disabling-certificate-validation

.decl TlsUnsafeGrandfathered(file: symbol, line: number)

Violation("COMPOSITE-DISABLING-CERT-VALIDATION", F, L,
  "TLS cert validation desactivee — MITM trivial, retirer cette option ou pinner le cert") :-
    TlsConfigUnsafe(F, L, _, _),
    !TlsUnsafeGrandfathered(F, L).
